@startuml
skinparam style strictuml
actor User
participant "Angular UI" as UI
participant "FastAPI" as API
participant "Agent (LangGraph)" as Agent
participant "Qdrant" as VecDB
participant "OpenAI" as LLM
participant "IMDBApi" as IMDB

User -> UI: Ask "What's the movie about dreams?"
UI -> API: POST /chat/message
API -> Agent: Invoke(AgentState with Query)
Agent -> LLM: Determine intent and tools
LLM --> Agent: ToolCall: RAG_Search("dreams")
Agent -> VecDB: Similarity Search Vector("dreams")
VecDB --> Agent: [Plot A, Plot B]
Agent -> LLM: Summarize/Match plots to movies
LLM --> Agent: ToolCall: IMDB_Search("Inception")
Agent -> IMDB: GET /title?name=Inception
IMDB --> Agent: Poster, Cast, Plot
Agent -> LLM: Generate Final Response
LLM --> Agent: "The movie is Inception..."
Agent --> API: Return Response
API --> UI: Present Chat Message + Movie Card
UI --> User: View Recommendation
@enduml
